# Keep build context lean and prevent stale local artifacts from
# leaking into image builds (most importantly TS incremental build
# state, which makes tsc skip emit when copied into a fresh image).

**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/.nx
**/.cache
**/target
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/coverage
**/.turbo
**/.next
.git
.github
docs
e2e
perf
hack
